**Game Master** | GM Group | joke
__Basics__
One or more Game Master(s) will occasionally turn into a host for a game.
While a host players may ping the specific Game Master(s) that are hosting.

__Details__
Pinging a Game Master will result in death, however when a Game Master chooses to host a game they become a host. 
The host is pingable and will not result in death.

Game Masters don't kill players that ping them, the player just dies.
